feat: v1.0.5 - Design and Game Analysis Update

Major Features:
- Enhanced UI color system with comprehensive theming
- Advanced chess board themes and visual improvements
- Opening identification and theory analysis system
- Enhanced move coaching with critical moment analysis
- Positional analysis board with interactive features
- Brilliant moves detection and highlighting

Backend Improvements:
- Advanced chess analysis engine with coaching comments
- Enhanced parallel analysis processing
- Improved analysis persistence and reliability
- Better error handling and performance optimization

UI/UX Enhancements:
- Responsive design improvements across all components
- Enhanced analytics visualization
- Better game analysis page layout and functionality
- Improved debugging tools and testing components

Documentation:
- Comprehensive color system documentation
- Opening identification implementation guide
- UI color quick reference
- Phase 1 testing guide
- Brilliant moves fix documentation

Testing:
- Added comprehensive test suites for utilities
- Enhanced component testing coverage
- Improved test organization and structure
